      <h2>Before you start</h2>

<p>It costs &pound;2.50 to amend a charge and &pound;10 to refund one. (There is no cost to refund a LEZ charge.)</p>

<p>You'll need:</p>

<ul>
	<li>Your receipt number</li>
	<li>The start date of the charge</li>
	<li>The number plate (Vehicle Registration Mark) of the vehicle you have paid for</li>
</ul>

<p>You will also need a credit or debit card to pay for any amendments.</p>

<p><strong>Single day charges can't be refunded</strong>, apart from LEZ charges.</p>

<ul>
	<li>Amendments can start from today's date</li>
	<li>Refunds are only available for dates in the future - you can't apply for a refund for today or dates in the past</li>
</ul>

<p>If you paid a charge when signed into your account, you must also sign in to amend or refund it.</p>
      
           
      
